You are earning money, you are already in a good position(thoughts by parents and relatives) and you wanna go abroad to study;

#ThankYouAdmission!

I learned a lot while preparing for it; I made lots of friends, people really helped me to develop my ideas; 

In the beginning of admission, there was kinda trash essays and at least we improved; Now, I have something to tell people in a good way.  In November, I almost cried, because, I couldn't even write my essay in a proper way; You supported me; 

I got my IELTS score in December(It wasn't good score, but anyway, tried for it and send to the admission).  I haven't taken my TRF, yes I have to go to collect.

Thank you everyone!

